## BADGES DE ESTADO — MAPEO COMPLETO

Usar este mapeo exacto. No inventar variantes nuevas.

```
OrderStatus:
  PENDING          → warning  → "Pendiente"
  PREPARING        → info     → "Preparando"
  READY_FOR_PICKUP → info     → "Listo"
  DELIVERED        → success  → "Entregado"
  CANCELED         → danger   → "Cancelado"

ProductStatus:
  ACTIVE             → success → "Activo"
  PAUSED_BY_SELLER   → warning → "Pausado"
  DISABLED_BY_ADMIN  → danger  → "Inhabilitado"

ReportStatus:
  PENDING   → warning → "Pendiente"
  DISMISSED → neutral → "Desestimado"
  RESOLVED  → success → "Resuelto"

isVisible (reviews):
  true  → success → "Visible"
  false → neutral → "Oculta"

isActive (usuarios):
  true  → success → "Activo"
  false → danger  → "Inactivo"
```

### Estilos de badge por variante
```
success:
  Dark:  bg #052e16, texto #22c55e
  Light: bg #f0fdf4, texto #16a34a

warning:
  Dark:  bg #451a03, texto #f59e0b
  Light: bg #fffbeb, texto #d97706

danger:
  Dark:  bg #450a0a, texto #ef4444
  Light: bg #fef2f2, texto #dc2626

info:
  Dark:  bg #0D1F3C, texto #5AAEE0
  Light: bg #E8F4FD, texto #1A3F7A

neutral:
  Dark:  bg #1f1f1f, texto #9ca3af
  Light: bg #f1f5f9, texto #64748b
```

